can you do me a solid and review my case

I had 6 month pretty clean and had a bad day... i just hit plat mmr and started to get the worst of the worst people again... no fantasy of getting my account back but man if u could set some precident on this one it would be helpful to the community....

i thought i was fine..... the removal of warnings led me to believe that i was being ok and clearly it wasnt. furthermore i feel like i shouldn't chat or be expressive at all.... i agree with the title of this page... we need voice chat to effectively gank up on toxic players like in cs go or dota.

http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-behavior-moderation/EU4nL1Ev-perma-banned-after-a-long-period-of-good-behavior

