the stuff you rioters go after people for is flat out childish. Just because you have the power to drop the ban hammer doesnt make it ok. You have a F2P game and are trying to moderate to this level?

please... just admit it that you guys have this system in place for the sole purpose of hoping peoples accounts get perma banned, thus they are more inclined to buy new skins on new accounts, raising your overall revenue.

There is literally no other reason for it... every sport in the world has taunting and badgering... when people cuss, as long as they arent racist... or OVERLY toxic, you people at riot HQ should grow up and cut the crap out

Your statistics are bullshit because they include the tens of thousands of innactive accounts people dont even play... alot of people get 1-2 bans on an account that is relatively "new" even at 30, and just make new accounts.

Truth is, your game by nature creates a toxic environment for the player base... outside of pro-play, there is no reason to take banning to the level that you do.

If you are that sensative, then i suggest you grow up, because the real world is vastly different from this environment you guys try to control like dictators, and its sickeningly pissing off your community

